info.p:
Set the ANT_HOME environment variable 
              to the directory where you installed Ant:



								export ANT_HOME=${ant_dir}

Set the CLASSPATH environment variable 
              for the Apache FOP application:


Set up your environment variable CLASSPATH to include the 
                  fop.jar, batik.jar and avalon.jar files in the FOP directory. 
                  For example: 
                  export CLASSPATH=${fop_dir}/build/fop.jar:${fop_dir}/lib/batik.jar:${fop_dir}/lib/avalon-framework-cvs-20020806.jar:${CLASSPATH}
